                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am not sure that charm as a whole needs to be re-worked.  I think that the converse is true that mobs that are charmable need to be re-thought.    
<br />

<br />
That is what happened with the change to Gates zones, the charming of certain creatures created an imbalance in play..  There are still creatures that can be charmed, after the change.  I know this for a fact as I had them show me after reading some of these threads.
<br />

<br />
The change should have been announced before hand. Sometimes things slip past and I do not get a chance to announce them.  For that I apologize as I know this was a MAJOR frustration.  I will try to make sure that does this not happen again. 
<br />

<br />
Brenlo</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
